cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD, cs.CE 

The paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques to study the uncertainty in numerical weather prediction models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.SD (Software Engineering), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
